            , on the 3d Instant. The Prosecutor swore, he saw the Prisoner come down his stairs with a Bundle; and tho' he knew that Woman had no Business in his house, being surprized, he let her pass by him, and go out; but going up to see if he had lost any thing, he found no Sheets upon his Bed; upon which he and a Friend followed her, and overtook her with them in her Apron; which his Wife swore to be theirs, and that one was taken out of a Closet in the same Chamber. The prisoner said she truck'd Earthen-Ware for them with a Woman in the Street, but cou'd not prove it. The Jury found her <rs id="t17161010-6-verdict28" type="verdictDescription">
